WEBVTT

00:00.723 --> 00:05.354
Sync and corrections by n17t01
www.addic7ed.com

00:05.740 --> 00:08.833
PRESIDENT REAGAN: <i>Air and naval
forces of the United States</i>

00:08.900 --> 00:11.695
<i>launched a series of strikes</i>
<i>against terrorist facilities...</i>

00:11.762 --> 00:14.322
REPORTER: <i>Pan Am Flight 103 crashed
into the town of Lockerbie.</i>

00:14.389 --> 00:16.029
REAGAN: <i>He has sanctioned
acts of terror</i>

00:16.030 --> 00:17.550
<i>in Africa, Europe and the Middle East.</i>

00:17.551 --> 00:19.231
PRESIDENT GEORGE H.W.
BUSH: <i>This will not</i>

00:19.232 --> 00:20.737
<i>stand, this aggression
against, uh, Kuwait.</i>

00:20.804 --> 00:22.339
REAGAN: <i>This relentless
pursuit of terror.</i>

00:22.340 --> 00:24.620
PRESIDENT GEORGE W. BUSH:
<i>We will make no distinction...</i>

00:24.621 --> 00:26.061
REPORTER:
<i>The USS</i> Cole <i>was attacked</i>

00:26.062 --> 00:27.502
<i>while refueling in the port of Aden.</i>

00:27.503 --> 00:28.663
This was an act of terrorism.

00:28.664 --> 00:31.096
It was a despicable and cowardly act.

00:31.164 --> 00:33.248
<i>The next samba</i>
<i>we're going to swing for you</i>

00:33.249 --> 00:34.569
is one of the good old favorites.

00:34.637 --> 00:37.071
...until something stops him.

00:37.138 --> 00:39.939
CARRIE: <i>I'm just making sure</i>
<i>we don't get hit again.</i>

00:40.007 --> 00:43.578
MAN: <i>That plane crashed</i>
<i>into the World Trade Center.</i>

00:44.948 --> 00:47.118
<i>Thousands of people running.</i>

00:47.185 --> 00:50.890
We must and we will remain
vigilant at home and abroad.

00:50.958 --> 00:53.025
(speaking Arabic)

00:57.699 --> 00:59.900
SAUL:
<i>What the fuck are you doing?</i>

00:59.968 --> 01:01.904
Fuck!

01:01.972 --> 01:03.907
CARRIE: <i>I missed</i>
<i>something once before.</i>

01:03.974 --> 01:06.710
<i>I won't...</i>
<i>I</i> can't <i>let that happen again.</i>

01:08.012 --> 01:10.314
SAUL:
<i>It was ten years ago.</i>

01:10.381 --> 01:11.849
<i>Everyone missed something that day.</i>

01:11.917 --> 01:13.818
CARRIE:
<i>Everyone's not me.</i>

